West Nile fever, Greece
-----------------------
Information received on 1 Aug 2017 from Mrs Chrysoula Dile, head, Animal Health Directorate, Ministry of Rural Development and Food, ATHENS, Greece

Summary
Report type: immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 27 Jul 2017
Date of confirmation of the event: 27 Jul 2017
Reason for notification: reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 12 Nov 2014
Manifestation of disease: sub-clinical infection
Causal agent: West Nile fever virus
Nature of diagnosis: laboratory (basic)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country.

